\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \tab \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93No.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Have you ever met anyone who has had sex in an airplane?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93No, but what is stopping two consenting individuals from- \u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It just doesn\u8217\'92t happen.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \tab \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What aboutsex  on a riverboat?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 John was about to continue on about hypotheticals, but caught himself, and smiled.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Well\u8230\'85before this goes any further, since you seem to want to get to know me, I think you might want to know that I work for Jakub Beksinski.\u8221\'94 As John said it leaned over the railing, twirled his hand, caught the river air and wafted it towards his nose. Behind his swirling fingers, Deborah spied her pontoon boat, floating like prey in the water. She could clearly make out her fellow lawyers and a few would-be jurors waiting for the fireworks.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Why would I want to know that?\u8221\'94, she asked. There was a slight unease in her voice.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Well, it\u8217\'92s just, there\u8217\'92s a general, violent hate for the man amongst your peers, so I thought you might want to know that I am his servant. I even helped to build The Experiment.\u8221\'94 }
