\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93How about this: You work for a consortium of Chinese companies who want to make sure that their interests are represented in the suit against my company. You are here to seduce me, then leverage the relationship in service to some nefarious purpose.\u8221\'94}
