\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I am trying not to think about it.\u8221\'94 She smiled annoyedly. \u8220\'93One or two more drinks and I think you\u8217\'92ll get there too.\u8221\'94}
