\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93How many are worried about it right now.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Deborah looked around the deck. The bartender was the only busybody onboard, but he was having a generally good time. A group of people out on the boardwalk had decided that the night would be better spent in the water, naked, and many others decided it would be best to watch. Looking over at her pontoon boat, she could see that she wasn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t missed there. They, too, were having a grand time.}
