\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Deborah, the world is about to change because of Beksinski. The world- you won\u8217\'92t be able to refer \u8216\'91the world\u8217\'92 as the container for all humanity anymore. I mean, it\u8217\'92s going to happen!\u8221\'94 His head was lifted up now, eyes raking the sky like a prophet. \u8220\'93In our time. We are going to leave Earth and fill up the universe.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m sure most people throughout history felt like they were living through the most consequential period of history, but the reality is that we will just absorb the change and move on, like we have always done.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \tab \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s precisely what I\u8217\'92m afraid of! That nothing will change.\u8221\'94 As he said it, he made a wide sweeping gesture, as if to condemn this boat and the people on it for having too good a time, apparently forgetting that his own drink was still half-full, and so the liquor inside splashed out of the glass and onto his white pants. He was already drunk enough not to notice. \u8220\'93I don\u8217\'92t like people, I don\u8217\'92t want us to pollute the universe with our broken institutions, our lack of foresight, our factionalism, our- \u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I understand, John, I do.\u8221\'94 Deborah stopped him with a pat on his thigh, pointing to where drink had spilled. She left her hand there long enough for him to notice the stain, and a little longer, for him to notice her . \u8220\'93But neither you or Beksinski get to make that decision.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Oh, shit.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \tab \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93The universe doesn\u8217\'92t belong to just you.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Deborah, once you open up pandora\u8217\'92s box you can\u8217\'92t close it. Before we start fiddling with the latch, we should be sure that the best versions of ourselves that we can be.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That day will never come.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That!\u8221\'94 John exclaimed, \u8220\'93Is a hypothetical situation, that-\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93John.\u8221\'94}
