\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Why not? It\u8217\'92s open and shut. We\u8217\'92re not violating any antitrust laws. We\u8217\'92re going to have a monopoly, sure, but that\u8217\'92s only a consequence of our hard work and historic accident, and you can\u8217\'92t regulate that. And even more, we\u8217\'92re under no obligation to license the use of our technology to anyone else. That\u8217\'92s the law.\u8221\'94}
