\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Then you know that any time there is a new technology that expands economic or military frontiers, your government, just like mine, will get involved and open it up. Besides, if Beksinski really did sabotage The Experiment like has been claimed, then this intellectual property case isn\u8217\'92t how they\u8217\'92ll get to you.\u8221\'94}
